<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
  </head>
  <body class="boys-bg">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="main-container">
      <section class="show-hero">
        <h1>The Boys</h1>
        <p>
          A brutal, dark, and sarcastic take on superheroes who are controlled
          by a giant corporation.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="show-details">
        <div class="info-block">
          <h2>Why I Love It</h2>
          <p>
            It completely flips the superhero genre. It’s raw, chaotic,
            and super entertaining.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
          <h2>Memorable Elements</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Homelander’s terrifying calmness</li>
            <li>The Boys’ crazy plans</li>
            <li>Dark humour and satire</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>